  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  females fulfilling the criteria of the ESHRE consensus 2011:

        At least two of the following three features must be present:

        (i) Advanced maternal age (≥40 years) or any other risk factor for POR; (ii) A previous POR
        (≤3 oocytes with a conventional stimulation protocol); (iii) An abnormal ovarian reserve
        test (i.e. AFC ,5-7 follicles or AMH ,0.5 -1.1 ng/ml).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  women who suffer from any other cause of infertility other than poor ovarian reserve

          -  refusal of the patient to consent for using her data in the study.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
